        <abstract>
            <p>His mother very ill.</p>
            <p>Mrs Hooker back from Bavaria.</p>
            <p>Hopes marriage [of Henrietta] went well. Is accused of saying he would rather go to two burials than one marriage.</p>
            <p>Has heard from Huxley who is threatening to "thin out" Mivart. Huxley is reading Francisco Suarez and finds Mivart misquotes or misunderstands him.</p>
        </abstract>
